@Bill
I really like that way of thinking about it, and I think my experience is similar. Although, I’m not necessarily talking about averages so much as the sweet spot for puzzle difficulty. I’m still under a year as a solver, so averages listed on my app are not very accurate, being heavily skewed by my early months as a struggling solver.

Also, your comment got me thinking… Is it considered bad etiquette to share solve times here?

